  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel serves a varied buffet breakfast with freshly prepared sweet and savoury options.</p>
<p>On half board you'll have a four course dinner in the hotel's restaurant which includes appetisers and a salad buffet. </p>
<p>A panoramic restaurant is located on the sixth floor of the hotel and offers traditional recipes including seafood and homemade pasta, with stunning views over the coast. A small bar is located of the roof terrace where you can enjoy cocktails and superb views.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
