  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pool &amp; Beach</strong></span></p>
<p>A small fresh water swimming pool is located on the hotel’s roof terrace (open from June to September) and nearby there's a whirlpool too. </p>
<p>The private beach (open mid May to mid September and payable locally) has sun loungers and a restaurant with drinks and snacks.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Activities</strong></span></p>
<p>There's lots of things to do in the area including the following activities that are payable locally:</p>
<ul>
<li>Mini Golf - 300m away</li>
<li>Bike rental - 300m away</li>
<li>Sailing - 2km away</li>
<li>Diving - 2km away</li>
<li>Tennis Courts - 5km away</li>
<li>Golf - 18 holes - 10km away</li>
<li>Horse riding - 10km away </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities </strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Parking (approx. € 29 per night, payable locally)</li>
<li>Fitness room</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
